videos.description: After Kevin Durant leaves the game with a calf strain Klay Thompson tells Shelley Smith that the Warriors need Durant to win it all, but "we can win one game without him."

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Klay: We ‘desperately’ need KD to win a championship) 2019/5/8

videos.headline: Klay: We 'desperately' need KD to win a championship

videos.description: Stephen A. Smith rips into the Rockets for their Game 5 loss to the Warriors and speculates about the severity of Kevin Durant's injury.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: KD's injury looked like more than a 'calf strain') 2019/05/09 ESHEET SportsCenter

videos.headline: Stephen A.: KD's injury looked like more than a 'calf strain'

videos.description: Mike D'Antoni believes the Rockets will bounce back and be ready on Friday for Game 6. A win in Houston would force a Game 7.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (D'Antoni: Rockets will ‘be ready Friday' for Game 6) 2019/05/08

videos.headline: D'Antoni: Rockets will 'be ready Friday' for Game 6

videos.description: When asked why he only took one shot after checking in with 7:08 left in the game, James Harden says he's not sure and has to go back and look at the game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Press Conference (Harden ‘not sure’ why he only took 1 shot in last 7 minutes) 2019/5/8

videos.headline: Harden 'not sure' why he only took 1 shot in last 7 minutes
